String.Source: Plus, the more outposts you've got nearby your target, the more interested they'll be in what you've got to say.
String.Dest: Plus, the more outposts you've got nearby your target, the more interested they'll be in what you've got to say.

String.Source: Put any back-up they might've called in in the dirt.
String.Dest: Put any back-up they might've called in in the dirt.

String.Source: If you've got some weaponry you don't have a strong attachment to, might be worth taking it with you to arm them up.
String.Dest: If you've got some weaponry you don't have a strong attachment to, might be worth taking it with you to arm them up.

String.Source: Knock 'em dead, boss.
String.Dest: Knock 'em dead, boss.

String.Source: Let's just get the first one squared away for now. Expansion can come later. So, what can I do for you?
String.Dest: Let's just get the first one squared away for now. Expansion can come later. So, what can I do for you?

String.Source: Be a couple of our guys waiting for you when you arrive. Help you clean the place out.
String.Dest: Be a couple of our guys waiting for you when you arrive. Help you clean the place out.

String.Source: You! You're going to start supplying Nuka-World! Understand?
String.Dest: Ty! Chystáš se začít zásobovat Nuka-World! Určitě to chceš?

String.Source: What? Uh, yeah. Sure. We'll, we'll make sure you're... taken care of.
String.Dest: What? Uh, yeah. Sure. We'll, we'll make sure you're... taken care of.

String.Source: Now, forcing a place to turn over provisions ain't complicated. Beat the locals so bad they don't want to fight anymore...
String.Dest: Now, forcing a place to turn over provisions ain't complicated. Beat the locals so bad they don't want to fight anymore...

String.Source: I'll send a crew ahead to the settlement.
String.Dest: I'll send a crew ahead to the settlement.

String.Source: But using tools from the Operators, building a Nuka-World transmitter within range of the settlement you're trying to target, they'll make it easier.
String.Dest: But using tools from the Operators, building a Nuka-World transmitter within range of the settlement you're trying to target, they'll make it easier.

String.Source: Back to what we were discussing...
String.Dest: Back to what we were discussing...

String.Source: Show those settlers who's in charge.
String.Dest: Show those settlers who's in charge.

String.Source: They'll help you clear the place out, take down any back-up these folks manage to convince to throw in with them.
String.Dest: They'll help you clear the place out, take down any back-up these folks manage to convince to throw in with them.

String.Source: Watch yourself out there.
String.Dest: Watch yourself out there.

String.Source: Yeah, yeah. Sure. You'll get your supplies, all right? Jesus.
String.Dest: Yeah, yeah. Sure. You'll get your supplies, all right? Jesus.

String.Source: I'll make sure there's a crew waiting when you get there and that they know they're only allowed to kill the hired help.
String.Dest: I'll make sure there's a crew waiting when you get there and that they know they're only allowed to kill the hired help.

String.Source: Expect we'll have a new meal ticket in no time.
String.Dest: Expect we'll have a new meal ticket in no time.

String.Source: Crew will be waiting for you when you get there. Help you deal with whatever you may run into.
String.Dest: Crew will be waiting for you when you get there. Help you deal with whatever you may run into.

String.Source: Give those settlers hell.
String.Dest: Give those settlers hell.

String.Source: Now, where were we on that job...
String.Dest: Now, where were we on that job...

String.Source: I'll send a couple gangers to meet you there, make sure they know not to kill the settlers.
String.Dest: I'll send a couple gangers to meet you there, make sure they know not to kill the settlers.

String.Source: I'll have some of our people meet you there to assist.
String.Dest: I'll have some of our people meet you there to assist.

String.Source: Don't have too much fun.
String.Dest: Don't have too much fun.

String.Source: I'll make sure you've got some back-up waiting for you. Help you deal with anyone this place manages to convince to throw in with them.
String.Dest: I'll make sure you've got some back-up waiting for you. Help you deal with anyone this place manages to convince to throw in with them.

String.Source: Settlers'll most likely call in some back-up. Stay sharp.
String.Dest: Settlers'll most likely call in some back-up. Stay sharp.

String.Source: A meal's always tastier when you ain't the one that had to grow it.
String.Dest: A meal's always tastier when you ain't the one that had to grow it.

String.Source: Lot of gangs have trouble with the whole "don't kill the hand that feeds you" thing. Rather just loot and pillage until they starve.
String.Dest: Lot of gangs have trouble with the whole "don't kill the hand that feeds you" thing. Rather just loot and pillage until they starve.

String.Source: More outposts you claim, the easier its going to be to intimidate settlements near them.
String.Dest: Čím víc základen zabereš, tím snadnější bude zastrašování osad v jejich blízkosti.

String.Source: Cripple the settlers, ice anyone else.
String.Dest: Cripple the settlers, ice anyone else.

String.Source: Just, don't let them kill you, boss. Wouldn't look good for the rest of us.
String.Dest: Just, don't let them kill you, boss. Wouldn't look good for the rest of us.

String.Source: Taking along some extra gear might be good if you want to arm up the crew.
String.Dest: Taking along some extra gear might be good if you want to arm up the crew.

String.Source: Time we put our mark on this joint.
String.Dest: Time we put our mark on this joint.

String.Source: Where am I going?
String.Dest: Where am I going?

String.Source: Need a little direction here, boss. Unless there was something else you wanted?
String.Dest: Need a little direction here, boss. Unless there was something else you wanted?

String.Source: Suppose I better get a move on, then. See you there, boss.
String.Dest: Suppose I better get a move on, then. See you there, boss.

String.Source: I'll give them a heads-up.
String.Dest: I'll give them a heads-up.

String.Source: If outposts aren't getting to where you need them to be, you could try building some entertainment like a Pick-Me-Up station, an amp and transmitter...
String.Dest: If outposts aren't getting to where you need them to be, you could try building some entertainment like a Pick-Me-Up station, an amp and transmitter...

String.Source: Sounds like places to sleep are in pretty high demand. Seen some awful things happen if people can't get their shut-eye.
String.Dest: Sounds like places to sleep are in pretty high demand. Seen some awful things happen if people can't get their shut-eye.

String.Source: Improved defenses is the word going around at the moment. Couple more turrets or guard posts ought to do it.
String.Dest: Improved defenses is the word going around at the moment. Couple more turrets or guard posts ought to do it.

String.Source: Beyond that, you could build them some entertainment - a booze still, Pick-Me-Up station, an amplifier if you've got a Nuka-World transmitter set up.
String.Dest: Beyond that, you could build them some entertainment - a booze still, Pick-Me-Up station, an amplifier if you've got a Nuka-World transmitter set up.

String.Source: Heard some nasty rumors about that spot. Think you ought to scout it out before we try and target it.
String.Dest: Heard some nasty rumors about that spot. Think you ought to scout it out before we try and target it.

String.Source: ... and food. Ideally coming in from a settlement you've convinced to hand over supplies, but you can always drop some direct in their workshop if need be.
String.Dest: ... and food. Ideally coming in from a settlement you've convinced to hand over supplies, but you can always drop some direct in their workshop if need be.

String.Source: I'm pretty sure a companion of yours resides there. I don't think they'd appreciate you hitting it.
String.Dest: I'm pretty sure a companion of yours resides there. I don't think they'd appreciate you hitting it.

String.Source: Sounds like they could use some more clean water. A purifier or a couple pumps ought to do the trick.
String.Dest: Sounds like they could use some more clean water. A purifier or a couple pumps ought to do the trick.

String.Source: Yeah. Getting word they could use some more food coming in. If you want to run a job to convince a new settlement to cough up supplies, let me know.
String.Dest: Yeah. Getting word they could use some more food coming in. If you want to run a job to convince a new settlement to cough up supplies, let me know.

String.Source: ... or a booze still.
String.Dest: ... or a booze still.

String.Source: Is there anything our outpost needs at the moment?
String.Dest: Is there anything our outpost needs at the moment?

String.Source: Don't think there's someone for us to intimidate at that spot.
String.Dest: Jestli si myslíš, že je tu v okolí někdo, koho můžeš zastrašit, tak se pleteš.

String.Source: That spot's a ghost town, last I heard. Maybe we can hit it once there's some bodies present, but can't do anything if there's no one there.
String.Dest: That spot's a ghost town, last I heard. Maybe we can hit it once there's some bodies present, but can't do anything if there's no one there.

String.Source: I think another group's already got that place in their sights. We can move in once they're wrapped up.
String.Dest: I think another group's already got that place in their sights. We can move in once they're wrapped up.

String.Source: Heard they're building some sort of crazy contraption there. Best to avoid that spot until all... that blows over.
String.Dest: Heard they're building some sort of crazy contraption there. Best to avoid that spot until all... that blows over.

String.Source: Actually, boss, sounds like you've got all the necessities taken care of.
String.Dest: Actually, boss, sounds like you've got all the necessities taken care of.

String.Source: Actually, I'd rather not target that one.
String.Dest: Actually, I'd rather not target that one.

String.Source: Got it.
String.Dest: Mám to.

String.Source: Check your Pip-Boy if you need specifics.
String.Dest: Check your Pip-Boy if you need specifics.

String.Source: Pip-Boy should be able to tell you which one.
String.Dest: Pip-Boy should be able to tell you which one.

String.Source: That one? So, that one's been sending us supplies. You sure about that's the one you want to hit?
String.Dest: That one? So, that one's been sending us supplies. You sure about that's the one you want to hit?

String.Source: Understood, boss.
String.Dest: Understood, boss.

String.Source: Ought to hold them over for a while.
String.Dest: Ought to hold them over for a while.

String.Source: Just means there's a better chance we could run low on grub, which could end up leading to some pissed off outposts.
String.Dest: Just means there's a better chance we could run low on grub, which could end up leading to some pissed off outposts.

String.Source: There a problem with that?
String.Dest: There a problem with that?

String.Source: Unfortunately, aren't any good targets to hit up for supplies, but you can always drop food you harvest yourself in their workshop.
String.Dest: Unfortunately, aren't any good targets to hit up for supplies, but you can always drop food you harvest yourself in their workshop.

String.Source: Your Pip-Boy should have more specifics.
String.Dest: Your Pip-Boy should have more specifics.

String.Source: Pretty sure that spot has been sending supplies to our outposts. You sure that's the one?
String.Dest: Pretty sure that spot has been sending supplies to our outposts. You sure that's the one?

String.Source: Uh, you sure about that spot, boss? Think they've been supplying our outposts.
String.Dest: Uh, you sure about that spot, boss? Think they've been supplying our outposts.

String.Source: That model of Pip-Boy should actually have a specific page to let you see which outpost is in need. Should give it a check.
String.Dest: That model of Pip-Boy should actually have a specific page to let you see which outpost is in need. Should give it a check.

String.Source: Uh, boss. That's one of the places providing us with supplies. You sure you want to target them?
String.Dest: Uh, boss. That's one of the places providing us with supplies. You sure you want to target them?

String.Source: You do as I say, understand? That's the target.
String.Dest: You do as I say, understand? That's the target.

String.Source: Getting word that your people could use more food.
String.Dest: Getting word that your people could use more food.

String.Source: That's the target.
String.Dest: That's the target.

String.Source: Probably only want to target those spots if you absolutely have to. So, that still the spot?
String.Dest: Probably only want to target those spots if you absolutely have to. So, that still the spot?

String.Source: That one's not going to work. No targets. Might be you'll have to make some adjustments before we can do it.
String.Dest: That one's not going to work. No targets. Might be you'll have to make some adjustments before we can do it.

String.Source: Uh, boss, think you're going to need to pick someone who didn't turn on you. How about another gang?
String.Dest: Uh, boss, think you're going to need to pick someone who didn't turn on you. How about another gang?

String.Source: Actually, doesn't look like there are any targets available for that job at the moment. Might need to do some prep work before we can run it again.
String.Dest: Actually, doesn't look like there are any targets available for that job at the moment. Might need to do some prep work before we can run it again.

String.Source: Hmm. Sorry, boss. Aren't any targets available for that one at the moment. You might need to run some legwork before we can do it.
String.Dest: Hmm. Sorry, boss. Aren't any targets available for that one at the moment. You might need to run some legwork before we can do it.

String.Source: That's not going to fly, boss, what with them turning on you. Want to pick another?
String.Dest: That's not going to fly, boss, what with them turning on you. Want to pick another?

String.Source: But is there something else, maybe?
String.Dest: But is there something else, maybe?

String.Source: Want to try another one?
String.Dest: Want to try another one?

String.Source: Something else, maybe?
String.Dest: Something else, maybe?

String.Source: Uh, you and the Disciples ain't exactly on speaking terms. You want to pick someone else?
String.Dest: Uh, you and the Disciples ain't exactly on speaking terms. You want to pick someone else?

String.Source: Actually, seems there aren't any more settlements to conquer. You ought to be proud. Made yourself one hell of a gang. There something else I can do?
String.Dest: Actually, seems there aren't any more settlements to conquer. You ought to be proud. Made yourself one hell of a gang. There something else I can do?

String.Source: Uh, Overboss? Something wrong?
String.Dest: Uh, Overboss? Something wrong?

String.Source: As soon as you say go, we'll go black and blue some settlers.
String.Dest: As soon as you say go, we'll go black and blue some settlers.

String.Source: Seems they brought in some muscle. Just means more fun to go around.
String.Dest: Seems they brought in some muscle. Just means more fun to go around.

String.Source: Chime in at anytime.
String.Dest: Chime in at anytime.

String.Source: Just some nuisances this time. Nothing a little firepower won't fix.
String.Dest: Just some nuisances this time. Nothing a little firepower won't fix.

String.Source: The Operators.
String.Dest: Provozáci.

String.Source: Brought us in for the fun job, huh? Putting down some settlers and their friends?
String.Dest: Brought us in for the fun job, huh? Putting down some settlers and their friends?

String.Source: Them settlers and pals are going to make for some good target practice.
String.Dest: Them settlers and pals are going to make for some good target practice.

String.Source: We're ready to terrify these settlers into submission and carve up their friends. Just let us know when you want to begin.
String.Dest: We're ready to terrify these settlers into submission and carve up their friends. Just let us know when you want to begin.

String.Source: Heard there are some settlers in need of a maiming. Sounds like fun. You want us to get started?
String.Dest: Heard there are some settlers in need of a maiming. Sounds like fun. You want us to get started?

String.Source: Sounds like a plan.
String.Dest: Sounds like a plan.

String.Source: Of course. I'll be here.
String.Dest: Of course. I'll be here.

String.Source: Bunch of pests have run of the place.
String.Dest: Bunch of pests have run of the place.

String.Source: Shank gave us the rundown. Rough up the settlers, kill the rest. We're ready to go when you are.
String.Dest: Shank gave us the rundown. Rough up the settlers, kill the rest. We're ready to go when you are.

String.Source: The hell? Fine. Just make it quick.
String.Dest: The hell? Fine. Just make it quick.

String.Source: Uh huh.
String.Dest: Mm hmm.

String.Source: We're all ready to carve up these idiots and their little friends.
String.Dest: We're all ready to carve up these idiots and their little friends.

String.Source: Those fools are already dead. Just don't know it yet.
String.Dest: Those fools are already dead. Just don't know it yet.

String.Source: You got some settlers you need roughed up. So let's go rough 'em up.
String.Dest: You got some settlers you need roughed up. So let's go rough 'em up.

String.Source: Bunch of pests wandering around the joint. Past due someone was sent in to do some exterminating.
String.Dest: Bunch of pests wandering around the joint. Past due someone was sent in to do some exterminating.

String.Source: Course. Take a look.
String.Dest: Course. Take a look.

String.Source: Takes some real stones to think you can take on all of Nuka-World and live. But, is there something I can do for you?
String.Dest: Takes some real stones to think you can take on all of Nuka-World and live. But, is there something I can do for you?

String.Source: Works for me.
String.Dest: Souhlasím.

String.Source: Sooner you put those traitors in the ground, the better. There something you need from me?
String.Dest: Sooner you put those traitors in the ground, the better. There something you need from me?

String.Source: Got it.
String.Dest: Mám to.

String.Source: Looks like they brought in some bucks. Should be fun.
String.Dest: Looks like they brought in some bucks. Should be fun.

String.Source: No more Disciples. Almost brings a tear to your eye. Heh. Made a real statement, boss. Now, there something I can do for you?
String.Dest: No more Disciples. Almost brings a tear to your eye. Heh. Made a real statement, boss. Now, there something I can do for you?

String.Source: Your call.
String.Dest: Your call.

String.Source: Uh, Overboss? Something wrong?
String.Dest: Uh, Overboss? Something wrong?

String.Source: I'll send word along.
String.Dest: I'll send word along.

String.Source: We're all set. No dead settlers, huh? Pity. Good thing everyone else is fair game. You ready?
String.Dest: We're all set. No dead settlers, huh? Pity. Good thing everyone else is fair game. You ready?

String.Source: Some nobodies and their entourage. Should be a fun kill.
String.Dest: Some nobodies and their entourage. Should be a fun kill.

String.Source: The Pack.
String.Dest: Šelmy.

String.Source: Wouldn't be surprised if some Minutemen showed up to lend a hand. Wish I could see their faces when they see who they're going up against.
String.Dest: Wouldn't be surprised if some Minutemen showed up to lend a hand. Wish I could see their faces when they see who they're going up against.

String.Source: Will do.
String.Dest: Provedu.

String.Source: Chime in at anytime.
String.Dest: Chime in at anytime.

String.Source: Shank told us what's what. Beat on the settlers, kill the rest. Ready to pounce when you are.
String.Dest: Shank told us what's what. Beat on the settlers, kill the rest. Ready to pounce when you are.

String.Source: Preparations are all set. You just let us know when you want us to get started crippling some settlers and putting holes in their friends.
String.Dest: Preparations are all set. You just let us know when you want us to get started crippling some settlers and putting holes in their friends.

String.Source: Just going to leave me in the lurch here, boss?
String.Dest: Just going to leave me in the lurch here, boss?

String.Source: Worth taking a moment to consider how much you like having that spot under your thumb. So, that the target?
String.Dest: Worth taking a moment to consider how much you like having that spot under your thumb. So, that the target?

String.Source: Just some filth. Ready to clean the place when you are.
String.Dest: Just some filth. Ready to clean the place when you are.

String.Source: Nothing much to worry about. Place just needs a good cleaning out.
String.Dest: Nothing much to worry about. Place just needs a good cleaning out.

String.Source: You hear? Apparently there's a big new contender among the Commonwealth gangs. Solid work, boss. Now, something I can do?
String.Dest: You hear? Apparently there's a big new contender among the Commonwealth gangs. Solid work, boss. Now, something I can do?

String.Source: Place has got some pests. Easy pickings.
String.Dest: Place has got some pests. Easy pickings.

String.Source: Nothing we need to worry about. Place just needs a good cleaning out.
String.Dest: Nothing we need to worry about. Place just needs a good cleaning out.

String.Source: You got it.
String.Dest: Jak chceš.

String.Source: Okay... Just make sure I have something sharp or heavy.
String.Dest: Okay... Just make sure I have something sharp or heavy.

String.Source: Figured those Pack loonies would go off the deep end sooner or later. At least now folks know what happens to traitors. Now, something I can do?
String.Dest: Figured those Pack loonies would go off the deep end sooner or later. At least now folks know what happens to traitors. Now, something I can do?

String.Source: Nicely done, boss. No one's going to step out of line after what you did to the Operators. Dimwits. Now, there something I can do?
String.Dest: Nicely done, boss. No one's going to step out of line after what you did to the Operators. Dimwits. Now, there something I can do?

String.Source: Those settlers think their backup's going to save them, they're dead wrong.
String.Dest: Those settlers think their backup's going to save them, they're dead wrong.

String.Source: Got some prey wandering around the joint. And I'm up for a little hunting.
String.Dest: Got some prey wandering around the joint. And I'm up for a little hunting.

String.Source: Any word on what the outposts might need?
String.Dest: Any word on what the outposts might need?

String.Source: Scoped the settlement out, boss.
String.Dest: Scoped the settlement out, boss.

String.Source: Boss. Took a look around.
String.Dest: Boss. Took a look around.

String.Source: Boss. I checked out what we're facing.
String.Dest: Boss. I checked out what we're facing.

String.Source: Hey boss. Got a look at what we're up against.
String.Dest: Hey boss. Got a look at what we're up against.

String.Source: Boss. Did a little recon on the target.
String.Dest: Šéfe. Trochu sem si proklepnul cíl.

String.Source: So you'll have more options using force. Also can't say "no" to firepower. You try chatting with a settlement, they might just tell you to take a hike.
String.Dest: So you'll have more options using force. Also can't say "no" to firepower. You try chatting with a settlement, they might just tell you to take a hike.

String.Source: Went and looked the place over, boss.
String.Dest: Went and looked the place over, boss.

String.Source: Fine by me.
String.Dest: Pro mě za mě.

String.Source: You got it.
String.Dest: Jak chceš.

String.Source: Sure thing.
String.Dest: Jasňačka.

String.Source: You got it, boss.
String.Dest: Jasně, šéfe.

String.Source: Sure thing. What'd you want to run?
String.Dest: Sure thing. What'd you want to run?

String.Source: Done.
String.Dest: Hotovo.

String.Source: Works for me. What type of job did you want to run?
String.Dest: Works for me. What type of job did you want to run?

String.Source: All right.
String.Dest: Tak dobře.

String.Source: Fine by me. How were you looking to do it?
String.Dest: Fine by me. How were you looking to do it?

String.Source: Boss. Something I can do for you? There another settlement you want to "help?"
String.Dest: Boss. Something I can do for you? There another settlement you want to "help?"

String.Source: Yeah, sure.
String.Dest: Jo, jasně.

String.Source: Yeah, yeah. What kind of job we talking here?
String.Dest: Yeah, yeah. What kind of job we talking here?

String.Source: All right.
String.Dest: Tak dobře.

String.Source: Can do.
String.Dest: To zvládnu.

String.Source: Deal. They'll be waiting for you.
String.Dest: Deal. They'll be waiting for you.

String.Source: Sure, sure.
String.Dest: Jasně, jasně.

String.Source: And did you want to talk the settlers off their land yourself or should I rally some bodies to help you put them on ice?
String.Dest: And did you want to talk the settlers off their land yourself or should I rally some bodies to help you put them on ice?

String.Source: I'll start getting that together for you.
String.Dest: I'll start getting that together for you.

String.Source: I'll make it happen.
String.Dest: I'll make it happen.

String.Source: Sounds good.
String.Dest: To zní dobře.

String.Source: Got it. So how'd you want to approach it? Talk them into leaving yourself or you and a crew putting some lead in them?
String.Dest: Got it. So how'd you want to approach it? Talk them into leaving yourself or you and a crew putting some lead in them?

String.Source: Good as done.
String.Dest: Jako by se stalo.

String.Source: I'm in no hurry.
String.Dest: I'm in no hurry.

String.Source: Mhmm.
String.Dest: Mhmm.

String.Source: All right. How'd you want to do it?
String.Dest: All right. How'd you want to do it?

String.Source: Just need the details.
String.Dest: Just need the details.

String.Source: Storming the power plant. The hell they think they're going to accomplish?
String.Dest: Storming the power plant. The hell they think they're going to accomplish?

String.Source: Current job can wait until you've... tended to the matters at hand.
String.Dest: Current job can wait until you've... tended to the matters at hand.

String.Source: Current job can wait until you've... tended to the matters at hand.
String.Dest: Current job can wait until you've... tended to the matters at hand.

String.Source: Land's yours, okay?
String.Dest: Land's yours, okay?

String.Source: Not gonna bother ya, all right?
String.Dest: Not gonna bother ya, all right?

String.Source: Get going.
String.Dest: Do toho.

String.Source: Keep walking.
String.Dest: Keep walking.

String.Source: Sooner things get taken care of in Nuka-World, the better. There something I can do for you in the interim?
String.Dest: Sooner things get taken care of in Nuka-World, the better. There something I can do for you in the interim?

String.Source: I'm going. I'm going... jerk.
String.Dest: I'm going. I'm going... jerk.

String.Source: Hanging from a hook's the only place for traitors.
String.Dest: Hanging from a hook's the only place for traitors.

String.Source: Hanging from a hook's the only place for traitors.
String.Dest: Hanging from a hook's the only place for traitors.

String.Source: Storming the power plant. The hell they think they're going to accomplish?
String.Dest: Storming the power plant. The hell they think they're going to accomplish?

String.Source: Should really get back, boss. Sounds like the gangs need some... guidance. But, there something you need from me?
String.Dest: Should really get back, boss. Sounds like the gangs need some... guidance. But, there something you need from me?

String.Source: Get outta here.
String.Dest: Vypadni odsud.

String.Source: Hey you.
String.Dest: Hej, ty.

String.Source: And if you're wondering what they're lacking, best thing to do is check your Pip-Boy.
String.Dest: And if you're wondering what they're lacking, best thing to do is check your Pip-Boy.

String.Source: Hey.
String.Dest: Ahoj.

String.Source: Rally some bodies. We're going to beat a settlement into supplying us.
String.Dest: Rally some bodies. We're going to beat a settlement into supplying us.

String.Source: Got it.
String.Dest: Mám to.

String.Source: Well, all right.
String.Dest: Well, all right.

String.Source: About time I talked some settlers into providing us with supplies.
String.Dest: About time I talked some settlers into providing us with supplies.

String.Source: Put the fear in them.
String.Dest: Put the fear in them.

String.Source: Get me a crew. That settlement's not going to know what hit them.
String.Dest: Get me a crew. That settlement's not going to know what hit them.

String.Source: Was hoping you could arrange a job for me.
String.Dest: Was hoping you could arrange a job for me.

String.Source: I want to convince a new settlement to start coughing up supplies.
String.Dest: I want to convince a new settlement to start coughing up supplies.

String.Source: I'll run them off their land myself.
String.Dest: I'll run them off their land myself.

String.Source: Looking to run a job.
String.Dest: Looking to run a job.

String.Source: I'll convince them to leave.
String.Dest: I'll convince them to leave.

String.Source: Start organizing a crew. We're going to bury those settlers.
String.Dest: Start organizing a crew. We're going to bury those settlers.

String.Source: Put the word out. Me and a crew are going to convince some settlers to start paying up.
String.Dest: Put the word out. Me and a crew are going to convince some settlers to start paying up.

String.Source: I want to claim another outpost for our gangs.
String.Dest: I want to claim another outpost for our gangs.

String.Source: It's time we took over another settlement.
String.Dest: Je čas, abychom převzali další řešení.

String.Source: Should probably wrap up making this first batch happy, boss. Then we can start looking to the horizon. Now, there another job you're interested in doing?
String.Dest: Should probably wrap up making this first batch happy, boss. Then we can start looking to the horizon. Now, there another job you're interested in doing?

String.Source: Hey there, boss. You looking for me to set up a couple jobs so we can start claiming those two outposts? Or did you need something else?
String.Dest: Hey there, boss. You looking for me to set up a couple jobs so we can start claiming those two outposts? Or did you need something else?

String.Source: It's got a page with all the information you could need on what your outpost might want. I'm also willing to share whatever I hear.
String.Dest: It's got a page with all the information you could need on what your outpost might want. I'm also willing to share whatever I hear.

String.Source: Hey, boss. Just one more outpost to claim. You want me to set up that job, you just say. So, what do you need?
String.Dest: Hey, boss. Just one more outpost to claim. You want me to set up that job, you just say. So, what do you need?

String.Source: And lastly... don't make them farm. Lose a lot of goodwill from your gangs by making them pick fruit.
String.Dest: And lastly... don't make them farm. Lose a lot of goodwill from your gangs by making them pick fruit.

String.Source: Now, you're not going to be able to take a direct route to the place - fast way to get yourself killed - so you'll have to meet our folks outside town.
String.Dest: Now, you're not going to be able to take a direct route to the place - fast way to get yourself killed - so you'll have to meet our folks outside town.

String.Source: Think we should put claiming those new outpost to bed first. So, if there's something else I can take care of, you just say so.
String.Dest: Think we should put claiming those new outpost to bed first. So, if there's something else I can take care of, you just say so.

String.Source: Ought to take care of those new outposts first, boss. Then we can talk supplies. Now if there's something I can set up for you, you just let me know.
String.Dest: Ought to take care of those new outposts first, boss. Then we can talk supplies. Now if there's something I can set up for you, you just let me know.

String.Source: Welcome back, boss.
String.Dest: Welcome back, boss.

String.Source: Back again.
String.Dest: Back again.

String.Source: Boss.
String.Dest: Šéf.

String.Source: Careful with anything you get from the Operators. Some Disciple tried to brew up one of their serums once... they cleaned her up with a broom.
String.Dest: Careful with anything you get from the Operators. Some Disciple tried to brew up one of their serums once... they cleaned her up with a broom.

String.Source: More outposts you claim, the easier its going to be to intimidate settlements near them.
String.Dest: Čím víc základen zabereš, tím snadnější bude zastrašování osad v jejich blízkosti.

String.Source: Lot of gangs have trouble with the whole "don't kill the hand that feeds you" thing. Rather just loot and pillage until they starve.
String.Dest: Lot of gangs have trouble with the whole "don't kill the hand that feeds you" thing. Rather just loot and pillage until they starve.
